not only where we are, but
to see that there are many,

00:06:32.580 --> 00:06:35.340
many years of interesting research and
development ahead of us.

00:06:35.340 --> 00:06:39.090
So maybe some students
will decide to join that,

00:06:39.090 --> 00:06:40.530
which would be a great result.

00:06:40.530 --> 00:06:41.520
So thank you very much.

